#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn32.2"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn32.2:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 32 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 32 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn32.2:0.2"
msgid "1. Valāhakavagga "
msgstr "1. Gods of the Clouds "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn32.2:0.3"
msgid "2. Sucaritasutta "
msgstr "2. Good Conduct "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn32.2:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn32.2:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Seated to one side, that mendicant said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn32.2:1.3"
msgid "“ko nu kho, bhante, hetu, ko paccayo, yena midhekacco kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā valāhakakāyikānaṃ devānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjatī”ti? "
msgstr "“Sir, what is the cause, what is the reason why someone, when their body breaks up, after death, is reborn in the company of the gods of the clouds?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn32.2:1.4"
msgid "“Idha, bhikkhu, ekacco kāyena sucaritaṃ carati, vācāya sucaritaṃ carati, manasā sucaritaṃ carati. "
msgstr "“Mendicant, it’s when someone does good things by way of body, speech, and mind. "

msgctxt "sn32.2:1.5"
msgid "Tassa sutaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "And they’ve heard: "

msgctxt "sn32.2:1.6"
msgid "‘valāhakakāyikā devā dīghāyukā vaṇṇavanto sukhabahulā’ti. "
msgstr "‘The gods of the clouds are long-lived, beautiful, and very happy.’ "

msgctxt "sn32.2:1.7"
msgid "Tassa evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "They think: "

msgctxt "sn32.2:1.8"
msgid "‘aho vatāhaṃ kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā valāhakakāyikānaṃ devānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjeyyan’ti. "
msgstr "‘If only, when my body breaks up, after death, I would be reborn in the company of the gods of the clouds!’ "

msgctxt "sn32.2:1.9"
msgid "So kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā valāhakakāyikānaṃ devānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjati. "
msgstr "When their body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in the company of the gods of the clouds. "

msgctxt "sn32.2:1.10"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhu, hetu, ayaṃ paccayo, yena midhekacco kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā valāhakakāyikānaṃ devānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjatī”ti. "
msgstr "This is the cause, this is the reason why someone, when their body breaks up, after death, is reborn in the company of the gods of the clouds.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn32.2:1.11"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

